#: src/plugin.php
msgid "Restore websites from the <strong>Wayback Machine</strong> with high accuracy. Download archived sites, remove ads and trackers, optimize images, and get a fully functional copy powered by the free <strong>Archivarix CMS</strong>. Trusted by thousands of users worldwide since 2017 for website recovery, migration, and SEO projects."
msgstr "Restaure sitios web desde la <strong>Wayback Machine</strong> con alta precision. Descargue sitios archivados, elimine anuncios y rastreadores, optimice imagenes y obtenga una copia completamente funcional con el <strong>Archivarix CMS</strong> gratuito. De confianza para miles de usuarios en todo el mundo desde 2017 para recuperacion de sitios web, migracion y proyectos SEO."

